\qj \fi720\li0\ri230\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin230\lin0\itap0 \fs20\lang2057\langfe2057\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp2057 {\cs16\fs18\super \chftn }{\fs18  As Sereni states: \lquote \'85
